chamelia hydropower electricity project is one of the large project in Darchula. it has capacity of 30 MW and is mainly situated in Shikhar V.D.C and village named as Balanch. this project is running from 2060 in slow motion due to unstable political condition of nepal and being in running phase till now. mainly this project is running in the financial help of government of japan, korea and gon itself. it has got about 85% acievement in construction works and civil works. 
by: dipendra bdr. khadayat (khwopa engineering college)


 

